    Ok, I dont know what exactly is going on because no one has filled me 
in...but here it goes...

    Aracnia, followed by Paralysis, and Aerostreak, entered the room....im 
guessing....and saw Kitkat being attacked by several Allience members. 
"Paralysis, cover Kitkat, Aerosreak get in the air!" She screamed, as he took 
out her bowcaster and fired.
    Megatron, along with Waspinator, Adrax, Tarantulas, Hell BEast, and 
Gremlin converged on Kitkats location. "Ah, I see you couldnt wait. Send my 
regards to Zardus, would you?" Megatron siad, as he and his troops fell into 
place, blasting any Allience member in sight.
